    "attributes": {
        "action": "We want the goverment to give us a bereavement day bank holiday",
        "additional_details": "I know that if we had a bereavent day bank holiday that would be a day for all of the uk to share and come together as one nation  ,and that would be a day that isnt bound by race or religion as we all have loved ones that have passed it would benifit by bringing freinds and families together and local buisness would also benifit to,we need the goverment to make this day happen as this is a day that everyone would want",
        "background": "People of the uk have holidays and bank holidays to celebrate mothers and fathers day ect ,but there isnt one day that caters for all of the uk ,due to different cultures of the uk  which i feel this is much needed",
